Introduction

Rino (리노) is a Japanese singer under LAPONE GIRLS, member of the girl group IS:SUE, and former member of its trainee unit CDL ∞. She was a contestant on PRODUCE 101 JAPAN THE GIRLS. She was eliminated in the finals, placing 12th. She was also a contestant on iCON Z ~Dreams For Children~.
